---
<footer class="bg-surface-container-low border-t border-outline-variant/50">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-6 py-section-py-desktop flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-12">
    <div class="space-y-6 max-w-sm">
      <span class="text-headline-md font-display text-primary flex items-center">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined mr-2 text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">landscape</span>
        Huella de Altura
      </span>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
        Transformando la agricultura a través de la tecnología Blockchain para un futuro más transparente y sostenible.
      </p>
      <div class="pt-4">
        <h4 class="text-label-md font-label-md text-primary mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">BOLETÍN AGROTECH</h4>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
          <input
            class="bg-white border border-outline-variant px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-body-md focus:ring-2 focus:ring-secondary focus:border-secondary outline-none w-full"
            placeholder="Su email corporativo"
            type="email"
          />
          <button class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-label-md text-label-md hover:bg-primary-container transition-all">
            UNIRSE
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h4 class="text-label-md font-label-md text-primary uppercase tracking-wider">MAPA DEL SITIO</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><a class="text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary underline transition-all" href="#inicio">Inicio</a></li>
          <li><a class="text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary underline transition-all" href="#beneficios">Beneficios</a></li>
          <li><a class="text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary underline transition-all" href="#sectores">Sectores</a></li>
          <li><a class="text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary underline transition-all" href="#">Contacto</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h4 class="text-label-md font-label-md text-primary uppercase tracking-wider">LEGAL</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><a class="text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary underline transition-all" href="#">Política de Privacidad</a></li>
          <li><a class="text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary underline transition-all" href="#">Términos de Uso Blockchain</a></li>
          <li><a class="text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary underline transition-all" href="#">Cookies</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-6 pb-10">
    <div class="pt-10 border-t border-outline-variant/30 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
      <p class="text-label-sm font-label-md text-on-surface-variant text-center">
        © 2024 Huella de Altura. Todos los derechos reservados. Tecnología para un Origen Verdadero.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant cursor-pointer hover:text-primary transition-colors">public</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant cursor-pointer hover:text-primary transition-colors">hub</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant cursor-pointer hover:text-primary transition-colors">account_tree</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>